Language name: BERTA
Language number: 4218
Alternate names: 
Classification: Nilo-Saharan, Berta
Comments: Triulzi et al. report all vowels appear long and 
geminate consonants also occur.  Tone and stress may both 
be contrastive.
Sources: 

Triulzi, A., Dafallah, A.A., and Bender, M.L. 1976. Berta. 
In M.L. Bender (ed.), The Non-Semitic Languages of 
Ethiopia. African Studies Center, Michigan State 
University, East Lansing: 513-32.